trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencyDatabase"></xref> objects.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection> uses the SqlCacheDependencyDatabaseCollection to programmatically access and modify the `databases` element of the `sqlCacheDependency` in the `cache` configuration section.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection>a SqlCacheDependencyDatabaseCollection programozott módon eléréséhez és módosításához használja a `databases` eleme a `sqlCacheDependency` a a `cache` konfigurációs szakasz.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.SqlCacheDependencySection>
